io.doov.core.dsl.impl.num

Class NumericFunction<N extends java.lang.Number>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.doov.core.dsl.impl.DefaultFunction<N,PredicateMetadata>
      • io.doov.core.dsl.impl.num.NumericFunction<N>
  • Type Parameters:
    N - the type of the field value
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ContextAccessor<N>, Function<N>, NumericOperators<N>, DSLBuilder, MappingInput<N>, Readable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DoubleFunction, FloatFunction, IntegerFunction, LongFunction

    public abstract class NumericFunction<N extends java.lang.Number>
extends DefaultFunction<N,PredicateMetadata>
implements NumericOperators<N>
    Base class for numeric functions.

    It contains a DslField to get the value from the model, a PredicateMetadata to describe this node, and a BiFunction to take the value from the model and return an optional value.
